                <header class="article-header">
                    <div class="article-header__inner">
                        <div class="article-header__head">
                            <div class="article-header__headline">
                                
                                <h1 class="headline headline--1 f-w-semibold">Become a Humboldt host!</h1>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="article-header__text">
                            
                                <div class="text">
                                    <p class="text--intro">Successful, inspiring science thrives on cooperation. Networks like the Alexander von Humboldt Foundation create the space this requires. If you are a researcher in Germany and would like to share this space, become a Humboldt host! You will be able to recruit researchers from all over the world as collaborative partners in your team at a research institution in Germany.</p>
                                </div>
                            
                            
                        </div>
                        
                            <div class="article-header__image">
                                <figure class="figure">
                                    <div class="figure__media">
                                        <div class="image loading" style="padding-top: 56.25%;">
