        <div class="text person-box__details" id="person-box-39223">
            <strong>Susanne Wegmann, Humboldt-Scout and DZNE group leader</strong>
            <br /><p>"As a scout, I have the opportunity to enable outstanding young scientists from less privileged regions of the world to connect to the global scientific community. This is a small contribution to global equal opportunities." <a href="/en/explore/newsroom/news/talent-scouting-in-mexico" class="link link--internal">more</a></p>
